                              Table "public.copy_history"
   Column    |            Type             | Collation | Nullable |      Default       
-------------+-----------------------------+-----------+----------+--------------------
 id          | uuid                        |           | not null | uuid_generate_v4()
 user_id     | uuid                        |           | not null | 
 product_id  | uuid                        |           |          | 
 platform    | character varying(50)       |           |          | 
 tone        | character varying(50)       |           |          | 
 copy_text   | text                        |           | not null | 
 metadata    | jsonb                       |           |          | '{}'::jsonb
 is_favorite | boolean                     |           |          | false
 created_at  | timestamp without time zone |           |          | CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
Indexes:
    "copy_history_pkey" PRIMARY KEY, btree (id)
    "idx_copy_history_created_at" btree (created_at DESC)
    "idx_copy_history_product_id" btree (product_id)
    "idx_copy_history_user_id" btree (user_id)
Foreign-key constraints:
    "copy_history_product_id_fkey" FOREIGN KEY (product_id) REFERENCES products(id) ON DELETE SET NULL
    "copy_history_user_id_fkey" FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES users(id) ON DELETE CASCADE

